column5: That things a beast for sure Mike
Walleyes in the Buffalo area are called "Yellow Pike"  But what you got there.....we call "Galvanized Pike".......and many other names....like crap heads....etc......  But it is a nice size one...
They put up a heck of a fight. But when you are expecting a ski or eye, they are a disappointment
Dang now that's a sharp only a scots man could love.
Nice vertical hold....  haha!  Those things are absolute brutes.  good job
Heck of a score Mike,that's the beast!!!
What a beast Mike!!!  Did you mention that Zack is only 3'6" tall? They are the silliest looking fish i've seen
